, 193.7053, 193.2132, 192.0809, 193.2035, 192.6836, 191.3343, 192.2424, 190.9497, 191.5595, 193.2114, 193.4206, 193.6129, 194.0728, 192.5539, 192.3091, 192.6516, 194.9236, 195.1044, 195.1169, 196.0068, 194.2172, 194.5491, 194.9727, 196.6837, 197.1083, 197.3081, 197.4778, 197.5611, 198.2324, 199.1888, 200.0981, 199.1092, 202.0693, 202.3004, 205.9486, 205.7649, 206.5506, 208.5297, 209.4151, 211.6075, 208.6109, 205.1074, 205.5845, 203.3538, 204.6688, 206.0691, 204.6573, 204.6443, 204.5664, 204.0439, 205.1944, 203.814, 203.2456, 204.2527, 203.7567, 202.5121, 202.7093, 202.7597, 204.9375, 206.9524, 208.5836, 209.0111, 208.3495, 208.6584, 211.067, 210.715, 209.204, 208.7259, 211.1012, 212.721, 213.8415, 216.5755, 212.5237, 209.9761, 210.114, 209.4178, 209.0969, 210.1558, 209.5391, 209.4568, 210.7791, 211.7805, 210.8497, 209.6009, 210.5289, 211.6519, 211.5802, 211.7812, 211.0477, 210.9234, 210.38, 207.7432, 210.9101, 211.5641, 211.9199, 212.2092, 212.786, 212.5662, 213.5412, 212.6983, 213.078, 212.1895, 210.38, 209.2756, 208.4965, 208.3375, 208.7717, 210.8937, 213.1657, 213.5976], "summary_html": "<h1>Weekly Momentum in Commodity Futures -- Factor Summary</h1>\n<h2>策略概述</h2>\n<p>论文发现商品期货中存在显著的短期动量效应（weekly momentum），与股票市场的短期反转截然不同。论文将过去52周分解为4个不重叠子区间，发现1周动量（CMOM_{1,1}）是最强且最稳健的因子，无法被carry、股票动量或套保压力解释。</p>\n<p>在中国商品期货上复现时，<strong>年度动量</strong>（CMOM_{52,27}，即跳过近6个月、使用前6个月的回报率）表现最优，Sharpe达1.19。这可能反映了中国商品期货市场的微观结构差异——更长周期的动量信号在A股商品期货上更有效。</p>\n<h2>回测表现</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (全期, 4bps)</td><td><strong>1.05</strong></td></tr><tr><td>年化收益</td><td>6.5%</td></tr><tr><td>年化波动</td><td>6.2%</td></tr><tr><td>最大回撤</td><td>-11.1%</td></tr><tr><td>日均换手</td><td>0.07</td></tr><tr><td>回测天数</td><td>3190</td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本内 2016-2025)</td><td><strong>1.15</strong></td></tr><tr><td>Sharpe (样本外 2025+)</td><td><strong>0.4</strong></td></tr><tr><td>半样本 H1/H2</td><td>1.14 / 1.16</td></tr></table></div>\n<p><strong>年度 Sharpe</strong>:</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>年份</th><th>2013</th><th>2014</th><th>2015</th><th>2016</th><th>2017</th><th>2018</th><th>2019</th><th>2020</th><th>2021</th><th>2022</th><th>2023</th><th>2024</th><th>2025</th><th>2026</th></tr><tr><td>Sharpe</td><td>0.97</td><td>1.28</td><td>0.8</td><td><span class=\"sh-neg\">-0.02</span></td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.73</span></td><td>1.01</td><td>0.2</td><td><span class=\"sh-hi\">2.7</span></td><td>0.55</td><td>0.4</td><td>1.11</td><td>0.27</td><td>1.91</td><td>0.17</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数据字段依赖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>字段</th><th>说明</th><th>必需</th></tr><tr><td><code>close</code></td><td>收盘价</td><td>是</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>信号更新频率</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>调仓周期</strong>: 每 5 个交易日</li>\n<li><strong>信号更新</strong>: 每日计算，每 5 天生效</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>品种覆盖</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table><tr><th>指标</th><th>值</th></tr><tr><td>覆盖品种数</td><td>57</td></tr><tr><td>回测交易日</td><td>3192</td></tr><tr><td>非零仓位占比</td><td>40.9%</td></tr><tr><td>日均持仓品种</td><td>15.7</td></tr></table></div>\n<h2>数学公式</h2>\n<p>论文定义四种动量信号：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{CMOM}_{k_1, k_2} = \\text{sort commodities by} \\sum_{t=t_0-k_1}^{t_0-k_2} r_{i,t}</div>\n<p>具体为：</p>\n<ul><li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{1,1}</span>: 过去1周收益（日频约5天）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{4,2}</span>: 过去第2-4周收益（日频约6-20天）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{26,5}</span>: 过去第5-26周收益（日频约21-130天）</li>\n<li><span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{52,27}</span>: 过去第27-52周收益（日频约131-260天）</li>\n</ul>\n<p>最优实现使用 <span class=\"math-tex\">\\text{CMOM}_{52,27}</span>：</p>\n<div class=\"math-tex math-display\">\\text{signal}_i = \\frac{P_{i,t-130}}{P_{i,t-260}} - 1</div>\n<p>截面排名后取top 20% long、bottom 20% short，IC-gate过滤弱品种，vol-target缩放。</p>\n<h2>改进历程</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>R1</strong>: 实现论文4种动量子区间 + combo。结果：yearly_mom_252d_raw Sharpe 1.19 最强，weekly_mom_5d_raw Sharpe -0.15 最弱。与论文发现的\"weekly最强\"相反，中国商品市场上长期动量更有效。</li>\n<li><strong>R2</strong>: 扩展参数网格（lookback x hold_days），添加12-1经典动量。yr_mom_h10_raw Sharpe 1.08，未超过R1最优。</li>\n<li><strong>R3</strong>: 细化quintile阈值（15%/20%/30%）、连续信号、IC-gating。yr_q20_h5_ic_raw 达到Sharpe 1.19，与R1最优持平。决策=skip（通过）。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>适用说明</h2>\n<ul><li><strong>数据频率</strong>: 日频</li>\n<li><strong>品种范围</strong>: 全品种（57个），黑色系（HC/JM/RB）和油脂（P）贡献最大</li>\n<li><strong>持仓周期</strong>: 每5天换仓，信号lookback 260天</li>\n<li><strong>已知局限</strong>: 年度Sharpe波动较大（2019/2021/2024偏低），说明长期动量在趋势不明确年份表现偏弱</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>验证状态</h2>\n<ul><li>corr vs Polars: 1.0</li>\n<li>Pandas 运行时间: 0.33s</li>\n</ul>"}